				</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->
	
				<div class="comment-content span7">
					<p>i think a degree simply tells a future employer &#8220;look for 4 years i was told by bosses (ie teachers) to go learn this or that fairly difficult task or subject and be able to regurgitate it on demand next week with a good degree of accuracy and/or understanding&#8221;</p>
